message.content: cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.HC. The paper deals with visual question answering (VQA) and proposes a new dataset and approach to improve VQA models' consistency and performance. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
